    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由Omno的制作人倾力打造，Kibu是一款沉浸式冒险游戏，带你深入自然之心探寻智慧真谛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193150/extras/ac8a2a2d934c364bc7948a612b8c0f03.poster.avif?t=1754313334\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193150/extras/ac8a2a2d934c364bc7948a612b8c0f03.webm?t=1754313334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193150/extras/ac8a2a2d934c364bc7948a612b8c0f03.mp4?t=1754313334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一位独居荒野的修行僧人。凭借手中法杖的力量在一系列令人惊叹的场景中攀爬、滑翔，杀出一条血路。与大地精魂对话，逐步重建你称之为家的倾颓神庙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越各具特色的奇幻之境，寻访远古精魂</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭晓隐秘于世的玄妙箴言</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用法杖滑翔、攀爬，征服蛮荒之地</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险途中搜集游鱼、盆景等稀世珍宝</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完美驾驭富有触感，且运行流畅的战斗系统来战胜敌人</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借诸神之力，将废墟重建成郁郁成葱的自然圣所</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
